lenders.name: Peter
lenders.loan_because:
I loan because I know how hard it is sometimes to obtain financing when you are starting a new business venture. Unlike Canada, there are many places around the world where people have virtually no access to credit, and even a small loan can make a big difference. Entrepreneurs are very important part of every society, and lack of capital and fresh credit in developing countries can hamper their ability to build a successful business.
 
In Canada where I live and work, it’s relatively easy to get loans for various purposes, and if you have a great idea and a solid business plan it shouldn’t be a problem to get a business loan. If I can offer similar financing conditions to even 1 person in a country where it’s hard to access credit, I’ll be more than happy.

lenders.occupational_info:
By day, I work in advancement at a private high school.  In the evenings, I formulate and handcraft artistically shaped 100% natural soaps in small batches using eco-friendly processes.  

I was motivated to become an entrepreneur myself by a desire to provide a non-toxic, detergent-free, all natural alternative to commercial soaps made with synthetic chemicals and fragrances.  I wanted to make soap safe for everybody, including loved ones with autism, allergies, and other illneses that cause them to react negatively to the synthetic chemicals in most soaps.  

My business has grown.  Thanks to my wonderful customers, I am privileged to be in a position to help other entrepreneurs and to donate a percentage of my company's profits to non-profit organizations that help people.
